  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Finance Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p>We’re looking for someone with a few years of finance and accounting experience as we\nscale our operations.  This role is ideal for someone who’s meticulous, proactive and enjoys autonomy – you’ll be working directly with the partners of the firm. </p><p>Scope of responsibilities:<br /><br />- Financial accounting and reporting for clients</p><ul><li>Maintain accurate and timely GL records and transactions</li><li>Prepare periodic financial statements</li><li>Perform reconciliations</li></ul><p>- Work with external consultants to ensure compliance to regulatory and tax requirements (e.g. tax agent, corporate secretary)</p><p>- Support partners in FP&A and budgeting for clients</p><p>- Assist and support partners in other business matters</p><p>- Occasional travel to Singapore for meetings</p><p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p><p>-  Degree in Accountancy or equivalent professional qualification</p><p>-  Minimum 3 years of relevant experience</p><p>-  Strong understanding of financial accounting principles, reporting standards, and regulatory requirements</p><p>-  Proficient in the use of Microsoft Office applications, including Excel</p><p><strong>About Cece Consult</strong></p><p>Cece Consult is an end-to-end accounting and finance company that strives to be the CFO partner for our clients’ growth journey.  Our client base includes small and medium enterprises (SMEs) in the technology and finance domains. Our partners’ have collective experience of over fifty years across finance and investments, helping to scale businesses in Singapore and globally.</p><p>For more info: <a href=\"https://www.cece-consult.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.cece-consult.com/</a></p>",
